{"sectionId":735,"sectionIdLiteral":"735","humanId":"lesson-314","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"I seek a future different from the past.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 314"},"annotation":"W-314","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-314\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"735#1\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"735#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>From new perception of the world there comes a future very different from the past.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"735#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>The future now is recognized as but extension of the present.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"735#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Past mistakes can cast no shadows on it, so that fear has lost its idols and its images, and being formless, it has no effects.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"735#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Death will not claim the future now, for life is now its goal, and all the needed means are happily provided.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"735#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>Who can grieve or suffer when the present has been freed, extending its security and peace into a quiet future filled with joy?</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"735#2\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"735#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Father, we were mistaken in the past, and choose to use the present to be free.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"735#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Now do we leave the future in Your Hands, leaving behind our past mistakes, and sure that You will keep Your present promises, and guide the future in their holy light.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"From new perception of the world there comes a future very different from the past. The future now is recognized as but extension of the present. Past mistakes can cast no shadows on it, so that fear","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 314: I 